@0 = ~Set into the basalt walls are doors of iron, molded in the visage of a damned soul. To look upon the door is to catch a fleeting glimpse of the horror Avernus offers all who find themselves lost within it.~
@1 = ~Ahead, you can make out the legions of Avernus marching in formation. To move forward will result in what is certain to be a painful and grisly demise.~